{"story":{"group_1":[{"bg":"bg_adv_21291.jpg","bgm":"bgm03_story08","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302801,"motion":100,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302001,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"Ayame","nameRight":"Himika","textLeft":"I heard about it while I was waitin' for@you.","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":302801}],"textLeft":"About how you gave him the \"rare blue@flower that can cure any illness.\""},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302801}],"textLeft":"And now he's completely better, right?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302001,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"textRight":"(She's not wrong, but that's not the whole@story.)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302801,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"So that's why I wanna bring 'em the blue@flower too."},{"chara":[{"id":302801}],"textLeft":"So they can get better as soon as possible!"},{"chara":[{"id":302001,"lipSynch":0}],"textRight":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301601,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Kokoro","textRight":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302801,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"Himika? Kokoro? What's wrong?"},{"chara":[{"id":301601}],"textRight":"Er..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302001,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Himika","textRight":"..."},{"nameNarration":"Himika","narration":"Even white lies can tear a family apart.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"This I know."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302001,"lipSynch":0}],"narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302001}],"textRight":"It's true that I gave my sick dad a blue@flower."},{"chara":[{"id":302001}],"textRight":"And it's true that he's healthy now and can@work again."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302801}],"textLeft":"Great!"},{"chara":[{"id":302001,"motion":100}],"textRight":"But it wasn't because of the flower."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302801}],"textLeft":"Huh?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302001}],"textRight":"Of course, I'm sure he was very happy to@get it."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302001,"motion":0}],"textRight":"But it wasn't the flower that cured him."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302801,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"Darn, no way..."},{"chara":[{"id":302001}],"textRight":"A flower that can cure anything? If a panacea@like that existed..."},{"nameNarration":"Himika","narration":"Then I...","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"id":302001,"lipSynch":0}],"narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302801,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"Himika?"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story01","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302001,"motion":100}],"textRight":"Uh, if a panacea like that were real, I'd be@a billionaire!"},{"chara":[{"id":302001}],"textRight":"Right, Kokoro?!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301601,"motion":400,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Kokoro","textRight":"[chara:301601:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]Huh? Oh, um, yes!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301601,"motion":1}],"textRight":"R-right... I mean, a panacea that can cure@anything?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302001,"motion":400,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Himika","textRight":"Seriously! It'd be worth so much!"},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302801,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302001,"motion":0}],"textRight":"What did the doctor say?"},{"chara":[{"id":302801}],"textLeft":"If they get plenty of rest, they should be@better in a day or two."},{"chara":[{"id":302801}],"textLeft":"But I want 'em to get better as soon as@possible."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":302001,"lipSynch":0}],"textRight":"..."},{"bgm":"bgm03_story09","chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302001,"motion":100}],"textRight":"Okay then! Let's go!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302801,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"Huh, huh, huh? Go where?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302001}],"textRight":"To the mountains!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302001,"motion":1}],"textRight":"Even if we can't find a flower that can cure@anything..."},{"chara":[{"id":302001}],"textRight":"You can give them other flowers as a@\"get well soon\" gift!"},{"chara":[{"id":302001}],"textRight":"I bet that'd really cheer them up."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301601,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Kokoro","textRight":"That's right. It's important that you share your@feelings."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302801,"lipSynch":0}],"textLeft":"...?!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302801,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"Yeah! You're right! Let's go!"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}